summary: Always believed that this area was a little lacking. Added a new wall section, some extra guards as well as some gear for those low leveled players.
descriptionHtml:
Always believed that this area was a little lacking.

Added:
- A new wall section
- A few more guards in the immediate area of the tower
- A few static props
- Staff, Spell book, Bow and arrows for those low level players.


First mod down unto the next adventure
author: Repsidy
